`8Keywords``   : Detect_Evil
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'detect evil'

 This is the ability to use one's will to see those that follow the path of the
Prophecy of Dark.  It shows such people by giving them a red aura to the
caster's eyes.

